description:
This is a 44 minute workout called '40 Min Daily Yoga Flow | Every Day Full Body Yoga For All Levels' from the channel Charlie Follows.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Welcome to your 40 min daily yoga flow. This class is great for all levels and focuses on the essential postures to build strength and improve your mobility.

This full body sequence includes options to suit all levels and is intended to give you a well rounded practice that you can come back to every day.

The sequence includes a steady vinyasa flow with hip openers, backbends, standing balances and side planks. It's designed to help you feel like you've given your body everything it needs to have a great day. 

I hope you enjoy this daily yoga flow. 

Charlie x
